Text: Re Employment CandidateJust to confirm that you have the right mail address to me Also to let you know that we have received Kristinas CVapplication and Michelle Kingsbury from my team will contact her shortly Kind regards Anna From Sara CT on CDT To Anna nron cc Subject Employment Candidate Anna Could I please have your email address Is it Also are you interested in receiving Kristina Fishers resume via facsimile Regards Sara Shackleton Enron North America Corp Smith Street EB a Houston Texas phone fax Forwarded by Sara ShackletonHOUECT on AM Sara Shackleton AM To Anna nron cc Subject Employment Candidate Anna I would like to fax the resume of Kristina Fisher to you I do not have a word version to email She is the candidate about whom we spoke recently I have also asked Kristina to visit the website wwwenroncareerscom and apply through that process I assume that you are the person who receives inquiries on the website Please advise me of your fax number and I can send the resume directly to you Thanks so much for your interest Sara Shackleton Enron North America Corp Smith Street EB a Houston Texas phone fax
